The '''2018 Brussels Summit''' of the [[North Atlantic Treaty Organization]] (NATO) was the 29th [[NATO summit|formal meeting]] of the [[heads of state]] and [[heads of government]] of the [[North Atlantic Treaty Organization]], held in [[Brussels]], [[Belgium]], on 11 and 12 July 2018.<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.nato.int/cps/ic/natohq/news_147856.htm| title=NATO Secretary General announces dates for 2018 Brussels Summit| date=20 October 2017| website=nato.int}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2018-06-06/trump-is-said-to-plan-july-trip-to-brussels-for-nato-summit|title=Trump Plans July Trip to Brussels for NATO Summit, Officials Say|last=Jacobs|first=Jennifer|date=2018-06-06|work=Bloomberg.com|access-date=2018-06-19|last2=Olorunnipa|first2=Toluse|language=en}}</ref>
