The '''Mineral Fire''' was a [[wildfire]] that burned in [[Coalinga, California|Coalinga]], [[Fresno County, California|Fresno County]], [[California]].<ref name=cdf/> The fire burned {{Convert| 7,050 |acre|km2|0}} of land. 

